            <description><![CDATA[【好消息！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%AC%AC8%E6%89%B9%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E9%9B%86%E9%87%87%E8%8D%AF%E5%93%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B756%25%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%AC%AC8%E6%89%B9%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E9%9B%86%E9%87%87%E8%8D%AF%E5%93%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B756%25%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#第8批国家集采药品平均降价56%#</span></a>】29日，第八批国家组织药品集中采购产生拟中选结果。此次集采有39种药品采购成功，拟中选药品平均降价56%。本次集采涵盖抗感染、心脑血管疾病、抗过敏、精神疾病等常见病、慢性病用药。其中，治疗甲流的<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%A3%B7%E9%85%B8%E5%A5%A5%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%96%E9%9F%A6%E5%B9%B2%E6%B7%B7%E6%82%AC%E5%89%82%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B783%25%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%A3%B7%E9%85%B8%E5%A5%A5%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%96%E9%9F%A6%E5%B9%B2%E6%B7%B7%E6%82%AC%E5%89%82%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B783%25%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#磷酸奥司他韦干混悬剂平均降价83%#</span></a>；常用降压药氨氯地平阿托伐他汀钙片降价48%。（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4884708602085432" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hcgy8a6jxgj60rn0fkdq902.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ByJ9onxflx084fJud7rO01041200ap6e0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680195491&amp;ssig=aAedlDJruM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ymI2obGElx084fJu8HSU010412005j8D0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;templa